metadata.name: Figure Graphic 1/1
metadata.description:
Connected attempts to let new forms of knowledge speak. A selective reveal of dangerous outcomes. What does a cypherpunk write? Fuzzy pullover crop mohair crew neck sweater top, feather detailing, puff sleeve gradient descent, suede front mixed print button up skirt, high-top laced sneakers. 

Synth Graph: a beautiful photograph of a tanned cypherpunk runway model with pink ombre hair wearing high fashion streetwear, knee high black converse, a fuzzy blue hat, a short red skirt and a black crop top, highly detailed. klms, steps: 75, scale: 13.
